    "content": "return ( ); \"use client\"; interface PlaybookPageLayoutProps children: ReactNode; : PlaybookPageLayoutProps) return ( /* Content */ children /* Footer */ ); // ✅ Server Component by default return ( /* Header Block */ Operations Playbook Performance Evaluation Framework How We Measure and Develop Our Team 1 . Evaluation Components Every team member is evaluated on 4 components with weighted scoring: Component Weight What It Measures A: Attendance 10% Days present, punctuality, leave compliance B: KPI Performance 40% Role-specific KPIs from individual scorecard C: Core Values 20% Demonstration of 4 company values D: Role Behaviors 30% Role-specific behaviors from scorecard 2 . Rating Scale (1-5) Rating Level Description 1 Needs Improvement Consistently below expectations; requires immediate attention 2 Developing Sometimes meets expectations but inconsistent; needs coaching 3 Meets Expectations Consistently delivers what is expected; solid performance 4 Exceeds Expectations Frequently goes above and beyond; role model in most areas 5 Exceptional Outstanding in all areas; sets the standard for others 3 . Evaluation Cadence Review Type Frequency Purpose Weekly Check-in Every week (15-30 min) Task progress, blockers, quick feedback Monthly Review End of each month Full 4-component evaluation, scoring, feedback Quarterly Review End of Q1, Q2, Q3, Q4 3-month trend analysis, development goals, career conversation Annual Review December / Anniversary Full year summary, compensation review, promotion decisions 4 . Final Grade Calculation Formula: (A × 10%) + (B × 40%) + (C × 20%) + (D × 30%) = Final Score Final Score Overall Rating Action 4.5 - 5.0 Exceptional Recognition, bonus consideration, growth opportunities 3.5 - 4.4 Exceeds Expectations Positive feedback, development investment 2.5 - 3.4 Meets Expectations Continue current path, identify growth areas 1.5 - 2.4 Developing Coaching plan, closer monitoring, support 1.0 - 1.4 Needs Improvement PIP required — See Coaching &amp; PIP SOP /* Footer */ Owner: Founder ); performance evaluation review assessment appraisal feedback rating performance review annual review quarterly review"
