    "content": "return ( ); \"use client\"; interface PlaybookPageLayoutProps children: ReactNode; : PlaybookPageLayoutProps) return ( /* Content */ children /* Footer */ ); return ( /* Header Block */ Operations Playbook RACI Chart Responsibility assignment matrix designed with maximum delegation in mind /* Delegation Philosophy */ Delegation Philosophy This RACI chart is designed with \" \" MAXIMUM DELEGATION in mind. Founder&apos;s Role: Participates in weekly meetings (R) Updates own scorecard (R) Makes truly strategic decisions that cannot be delegated (A) Gets informed on key outcomes (I) Consulted only when founder input is truly needed (C) EVERYTHING ELSE IS DELEGATED TO ROLE OWNERS. Each role OWNS their area completely: Operations Coordinator → Owns all client & project operations Marketing Specialist → Owns all marketing activities HR & Admin Coordinator → Owns all people operations Web Developer → Owns all technical work Finance Coordinator → Owns all financial tracking /* RACI Definitions */ RACI Definitions Letter Role Meaning Color R Responsible Does the work. Executes the task. Green A Accountable Owns it. Makes sure it gets done. Final decision maker. Blue A/R Accountable + Responsible Owns it AND does the work (common for role owners) Blue C Consulted Provides input BEFORE the decision or action. Yellow I Informed Kept in the loop AFTER the decision or action. Gray — Not Involved No role in this activity. White /* Founder's Limited Involvement */ Founder&apos;s Limited Involvement Category Founder Role Why Daily Operations I Not involved / Informed Fully delegated to Ops Coordinator Weekly Meetings R Participates (R) Attends and updates own scorecard only Client Management I C Informed / Consulted if escalated Ops Coordinator owns client relationships Marketing I Informed on results Marketing Specialist owns all campaigns Technical I Informed on major issues Web Developer owns all technical work HR & Admin I C Informed / Consulted on policy HR Coordinator owns people operations Finance I Informed on reports Finance Coordinator owns all tracking Strategic Decisions A Accountable (A) Only area Founder must own ); raci responsibility accountable consulted informed delegation matrix roles chart who does what assign ownership"
